<h1>Problem 1054 - 2011 IMOSL, A3</h1>
<h2 class='difficulty'>Difficulty: 7</h2>
<p>Determine all pairs \((f,g)\) of functions from the set of real numbers to itself that satisfy \[g(f(x+y)) = f(x) + (2x + y)g(y)\] for all real numbers \(x\) and \(y\).</p>
